@misslhommedieu offering this $15,750,000 Bel Air mansion (@1518belair) with over 9,300 sq ft including 6 bedrooms and 10 bathrooms - A true timeless masterpiece featuring the latest in technology, materials and infused with Old World-class and spectacular magic. Completely remodeled and completed in 2014. A state-of-the-art open floor plan, grand open kitchen/family room, and breakfast nook seating for 10. A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair

node.text:
@AmirHamzehali offering this $9,438,000 West Vancouver home - Welcome to 940 Groveland, nestled in one of the most sought after locations in the British Properties. Everything about this property shouts out perfectness, wide driveway combined with a great ocean & city view, 100 feet of frontage & 14620 sqft of rectangular south facing lot & most importantly more than 8000 sqft of perfectly laid out living space. No expense has been spared in this fabulous French Chateau architecture. The list is endless: 4 full bedrooms upstairs, Miele appliances, outdoor pool, hot tub & fire pit, 1000 sqft covered balcony, custom trimming & millwork throughout the house, home theatre, walk out basement & much more. Don't miss out on this opportunity, book your private showing today. Close to Collingwood/Mulgrave schools.

See @AmirHamzehali for more!
